    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Granted by @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.Duelist's Challenge].</p>\n<p>Select one foe that you can see and proclaim a challenge. That foe is your dueling opponent until they are defeated, flee, or the encounter ends.</p>\n<p>Any time you hit that enemy using a single one-handed melee weapon while your other hand or hands are free, you gain a circumstance bonus to the Strike's damage equal to the number of damage dice your weapon deals.</p>\n<p>If you attack a creature other than your dueling opponent, you take a circumstance penalty to damage equal to the number of damage dice your weapon deals.</p>"
        },
